OL,6,GThere was a little surprise for viewers
OL,7,Gduring BBC Breakfast this morning. The
OL,8,Gregional news bulletin at 7.55am has
OL,9,Gbeen reinstated without much of a
OL,10,Gfanfare.
OL,12,FAlthough this bulletin is shorter than
OL,13,Fthe others, it effectively means that
OL,14,Fthe regional news provision during the
OL,15,Fprogramme is now back to where it was
OL,16,Fbefore the pandemic.
OL,18,FThe early morning regional news service
OL,19,Fhas had something of a bumpy ride over
OL,20,Fthe past three years.
OL,3,CBBC regional news resumes pre-pandemic
OL,4,Cschedule at breakfast
