OL,6,FIn the dark days of March 2020 it was
OL,7,Fdropped completely. Opts in the nations
OL,8,Fresumed as restrictions eased before
OL,9,Fearly morning bulletins returned to the
OL,10,FEnglish regions ` though there were
OL,11,Flater occasions when English opts had
OL,12,Fto be dropped again.
OL,14,FIn the English regions there have also
OL,15,Fbeen a number of occasions when
OL,16,Fneighbouring services have been merged
OL,17,F` often though not always as a result
OL,18,Fof Covid-related absences.
OL,20,FBut with life now normal again, it
OL,21,Fseems right to be offering a full
OL,22,Fservice.
OL,3,CBBC regional news resumes pre-pandemic
OL,4,Cschedule at breakfast
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
