OL,6,FBut on the other hand the programme's
OL,7,Faudience peaks around 8am. The loss of
OL,8,Fthe 7.55am bulletin was significant to
OL,9,Fthe nations and regions. Hopefully the
OL,10,Fnew pattern is an acceptable
OL,11,Fcompromise.
OL,13,FThe regional news, weather and travel
OL,14,Fservice during Breakfast is one of the
OL,15,Fprogramme's unique selling points.
OL,3,CBBC regional news resumes pre-pandemic
OL,4,Cschedule at breakfast
