OL,6,FThe service is much more comprehensive
OL,7,Fthan ITV 1's equivalent ` three hourly
OL,8,Fbulletins of approximately one minute's
OL,9,Fduration plus a short local weather
OL,10,Fforecast which would appear to be
OL,11,Frecorded the night before, at least in
OL,12,Fsome regions.
OL,14,FRegional opts were only introduced to
OL,15,FITV's breakfast programme when GMTV
OL,16,Ftook over the franchise in 1993 whereas
OL,17,Fthey have been a key part of the BBC's
OL,18,Fservice since day 1 of Breakfast Time.
OL,3,CBBC regional news resumes pre-pandemic
