OL,6,FThese are not easy times for the BBC's
OL,7,Fregional news teams. Last week they
OL,8,Fwent on strike over cuts to English
OL,9,Flocal radio and action is possible too
OL,10,Fover cuts to Radio Foyle.
OL,12,FBut hopefully the importance of
OL,13,Fregional news during BBC Breakfast is
OL,14,Fnow clearer than ever.
OL,3,CBBC regional news resumes pre-pandemic
